de.weltraumschaf.neuron.node
Interface Node

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable, Observable
All Known Implementing Classes:
NodeImpl
public interface Node
extends Observable, Comparable

This type defines a node. Nodes may be connected to each other and communicate to each other.

Author:
Sven Strittmatter
